OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1772697873
OL,3,CBaby returned to wrong mother in mix-
OL,4,Cup at maternity scandal trust
OL,6,FMaternity campaigners in Nottingham
OL,7,Fhave expressed frustration that
OL,8,Fservices at Nottingham University
OL,9,FHospitals Trust, which failed their
OL,10,Fdaughter nearly a decade ago, still
OL,11,F"require improvement."
OL,13,FDr Jack Hawkins and Sarah Hawkins,
OL,14,Fwhose daughter Harriet died in 2016,
OL,15,Fresponded to the latest Care Quality
OL,16,FCommission report, saying that changes
OL,17,Fshould have been made soon after
OL,18,FHarriet's death.
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@VO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1772697873
OL,3,CBaby returned to wrong mother in mix-
OL,4,Cup at maternity scandal trust
OL,6,FSarah said "Harriet should be 10 in
OL,7,FApril," while Jack added, "How can it
OL,8,Fbe after several years, it still
OL,9,Frequires improvement?"
OL,11,FThe CQC inspection, covering City
OL,12,FHospital and Queens Medical Centre,
OL,13,Fwas carried out in May last year, but
OL,14,Fthe report was published after a ten-
OL,15,Fmonth delay.
OL,26,@nD@LOUoD@GO]oD@[OUqD@VO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1772697873
OL,3,CBaby returned to wrong mother in mix-
OL,4,Cup at maternity scandal trust
OL,6,FThe CQC apologised for the delay,
OL,7,Fciting changes to its technology
OL,8,Fsystems, and said the time taken fell
OL,9,F"far short of what people using
OL,10,Fservices and the trust should be able
OL,11,Fto expect."
OL,13,FWhat did the CQC report find?
OL,15,FThe report found that the service "did
OL,16,Fnot always keep women and babies safe."
OL,18,FIt identified gaps in staffing, poor
OL,19,Fsharing of lessons learned and staff
OL,20,Fnot always confident to raise concerns.
OL,26,@qD@AOUsD@KO]wD@cOUxD@gO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1772697873
OL,3,CBaby returned to wrong mother in mix-
OL,4,Cup at maternity scandal trust
OL,6,FInspectors also noted inconsistencies
OL,7,Fin monitoring room and medicine
OL,8,Frefrigerator temperatures, incomplete
OL,9,Fequipment checks and a critical safety
OL,10,Flapse in checking mother and baby
OL,11,Fidentification bands.
OL,13,FOne incident showed a baby being
OL,14,Freturned to the wrong mother,
OL,15,Fhighlighting a serious risk.
OL,17,F"It is disappointing"
OL,19,FJack Hawkins emphasised the severity
OL,20,Fof the issue, saying:
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1772697873
OL,3,CBaby returned to wrong mother in mix-
OL,4,Cup at maternity scandal trust
OL,6,F"The chances of something like that
OL,7,Fhappening are small but the impact is
OL,8,Fso massive, so it is disappointing the
OL,9,FCQC picked up there was a risk around
OL,10,Fthat."
OL,12,FHe added; "This is a department that's
OL,13,Fbeen under scrutiny for so long. How
OL,14,Fcome people are finding things out
OL,15,Flike this about them?
OL,17,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,18,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,19,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,20,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@FO]tD@KOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1772697873
OL,3,CBaby returned to wrong mother in mix-
OL,4,Cup at maternity scandal trust
OL,6,FDespite these failings, the report
OL,7,Fhighlighted some positives.
OL,9,FThe environment was largely considered
OL,10,Fsafe, staff knew how to protect people
OL,11,Ffrom abuse and women were treated with
OL,12,Fkindness and involved in decisions
OL,13,Fabout their care.
OL,15,FAnthony May, chief executive at NUH
OL,16,Fsaid;
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1772697873
OL,3,CBaby returned to wrong mother in mix-
OL,4,Cup at maternity scandal trust
OL,6,F"Whilst there are some very positive
OL,7,Fmessages in the report, there are also
OL,8,Fsome things that we must address and
OL,9,Ftake very seriously, particularly
OL,10,Faround safety and culture."
OL,12,FMr May added about the abduction
OL,13,Fpolicy; " 'We take that extremely
OL,14,Fseriously. Since the inspectors came,
OL,15,Fwe've reviewed the policy. We have run
OL,16,Ftwo test drills, which went very well
OL,17,Fand we've done more communication to
OL,18,Fcolleagues in the service."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@[O]uD@IOUzD@[O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1772697873
OL,3,CBaby returned to wrong mother in mix-
OL,4,Cup at maternity scandal trust
OL,6,FJack and Sarah Hawkins continue their
OL,7,Fcalls for a statutory public inquiry,
OL,8,Farguing that accountability is
OL,9,Fessential for real cultural
OL,10,Fimprovement.
OL,12,FWhile they recognise changes at the
OL,13,Fboard and ongoing efforts, Jack said,
OL,14,F"How can it be after several years, it
OL,15,Fstill requires improvement. It should
OL,16,Fhave been excellent."
OL,26,@vD@AOUxD@UO]
